this_title: The Many Faces of Beth Jones
introduction: Off the back of a successful stint on a television show, Beth's agent has been hard at work finding her new roles to make her a star. As she excitedly arrives to meet her agent, the parts found for her might not be exactly what she was hoping for. After a TV success, Beth's agent lines up new roles, but they may not match her expectations. Excitement turns to uncertainty in this comedic tale.
foreign_title: The Many Faces of Beth Jones
